/>\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"aed375af841264d8aa43400cec6fd391ead9d0a7","tid":1348162,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4181470ec71473103e547325e41df94c6f406185","tid":1348162,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"黑警同黑幫誓不兩立? 劃清界線？<br />\n<br />\n係咪想笑死我?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/tKje5GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKje5GX.png&h=43da8968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"594a611182d8be6117f00b743b9b0f440499f3ec","tid":1348162,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新一哥一定係黑記</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強與元朗社團關係<br />\n<br />\n行動處副處長鄧炳強是現時對付示威者的最高負責人，製訂沸水政策在旺角丶上水及沙田圍捕示威者，造成大規模衝突。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能唔記得，他在梁振英上場後，2012年出任元朗警區指揮官，同當地社團黑幫稔熟，離任時梁志祥丶錦田鄧賀年歡送。元朗黑幫一直是梁振英支持者，當日在朗晴村諮詢會曾樹和及一班流氓便公然為梁保駕護航。<br />\n<br />\n今日元朗黑幫公然在車廂襲擊市民，昨天消息已經廣泛流傳，今晚八點白衫流氓通街行，區議員丶居民報警冇人理，元朗警方絕對知情，他們是配合黑幫襲擊恫嚇香港人。我們有理由懷疑，究竟曾任元朗指揮官的行動處處長是否就是主謀？"},{"pid":"38c22e8b3844c0141ace94632f4c212a26de47ba","tid":1348162,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"大家都是黑社會 不用分得那麼細"},{"pid":"6b9442009f5d217c8cfc7be25ef0b7caed333f43","tid":1348162,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRY7Gfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRY7Gfh.png&h=22e9726d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKje5GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKje5GX.png&h=d0a8df42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金鐘對峙<br />\n元朗合照<br />\n<br />\n林鄭龜縮,政府無直接回應市民意見後果<br />\n今日香港既局勢,對立<br />\n完全係林鄭一手做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢係特首點會完全唔知無預視後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者會都轉身走, 睇得出佢係點回應市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e91f6353a3c38e9cef4565ba0f3b837e4068b7","tid":1348162,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e44cda36755cd2785508931ccc7ff10c57e398a","tid":1348162,"uid":255962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e9ae2bbb8c3da35a082f333eb2fcbda936ef17bf","tid":1348162,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"呢個係乜黎?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/tKje5GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKje5GX.png&h=74bc741b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"They connected."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"誤會左林奠喇, we connect 唔係同我地講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e64101258eb30658db838af43be394ad9e6364a","tid":1348162,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"唔同時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47735790902fdfabd1bcc82798455c658dc495","tid":1348162,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"白衫黑幫經過黑警防線離開南邊圍村<br />\n<br />\n黑警仲開路比白衫黑幫渣車走<br />\n<br />\n唔係警黑合作, 係乜呢?<br />\n<br />\nNOW TV影晒喎"},{"pid":"3ff186862a2bcb8c9036ec160f53c4affdd9179c","tid":1348162,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0334da2f036860f6f4bdbc92e9ad7ab26e857773","tid":1348162,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:4